  "texts": [
    "We train each of TacticAI's models in isolation, using NVIDIA Tesla P100 GPUs.",
    "To minimise overfitting, each model's learning objective is regularised with an L 2 norm penalty with respect to the network parameters.",
    "During training, we use the Adam stochastic gradient descent optimiser 33 over the regularised loss.",
    "All models, including baselines, have been given an equal hyperparameter tuning budget, spanning the number of message passing steps ({1, 2, 4}), initial learning rate ({0.0001, 0.00005}), batch size ({128, 256}) and L 2 regularisation coefficient ({0.01, 0.005, 0.001, 0.0001, 0}).",
